      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG ZEAL (5) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (20.01) behind End Of Era at Q Lakeside. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. One of the leading chances. FIVE BIRDIES (1) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (30.51) at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Well-placed to take this out. MAJESTIC ZEAL (2) is a safe beginner. Last start finished 4th in a Mix 5 on July 1 over 352m at Q Lakeside behind Arka Solar beaten 7 lengths (20.14). Can hit the frame with the right run. LUMBY (6) hit the frame here last start so don't underestimate.",
